{{! ---
component: article
============================================

Requirements:
- c-figure (only hbs)
- c-c-picture (only hbs)
- c-video (only hbs)
- c-c-rte (only hbs)

Options:
- articleContextClass {String} [default] - Just pass a string
- articleClasses {String} - Modifier classes

- articleHeader {Object} - Object which contains multiple elements
- articleHeader.articleHeaderClasses {String} - Class for header
- articleHeader.articleDate {String} - Date string
- articleHeader.articleDatetime {String} - Date attribute
- articleHeader.articleH1 {String} - Header H1
- articleHeader.articleH2 {String} - Header H2
- articleHeader.articleH3 {String} - Header H3
- articleHeader.articleIntro {String} - Header Intro

- articleFigure {Object} - Article figure object which contains data for figure (@see c-figure)
- articleFigure.articleFigureClasses {String} - Classes for figure wrapper div

- articleContentClasses {String} - Classes content div
- articleSummary {String} - You can define an article as teaser
- articleLength {Number} - String length for teaser
- articleMd {Object} - @see c-rte

- articleFooter {Object} - Object which contains multiple elements
- articleFooter.articleFooterClasses {String} - Class for footer element
- articleFooter.articleFooterLink {String} - Footer link

Important Notes:

--- }}

<article class="c-article{{#if articleContextClass}}--{{articleContextClass}}{{else}}--default{{/if}}{{#if articleClasses}} {{articleClasses}}{{/if}}" data-css="c-article">

	{{#if articleHeader}}
		<header class="article__header{{#if articleHeaderClasses}} {{articleHeaderClasses}}{{/if}}">
			{{> c-article__header articleHeader}}
		</header>
	{{/if}}

	{{#if articleFigure }}
		<div class="article__figure{{#if articleFigureClasses}} {{articleFigureClasses}}{{/if}}">
			{{> c-figure articleFigure}}
		</div>
	{{/if}}

	<div class="article__content{{#if articleContentClasses}} {{articleContentClasses}}{{/if}}">
		{{#if articleSummary}}
			{{{truncate articleSummary articleLength "..." }}}
		{{else}}
			{{#with articleMd}}
				{{> c-rte}}
			{{/with}}
		{{/if}}
	</div>

	{{#if articleFooter}}
		<footer class="article__footer {{articleFooterClasses}}">
			{{> c-article__footer articleFooter}}
		</footer>
	{{/if}}

</article>